256
00:16:30,160 --> 00:16:31,070
[I know.]

257
00:16:32,950 --> 00:16:34,070
[I know it all.]

258
00:16:41,500 --> 00:16:42,390
Ms Wu Yan, you are here.

259
00:16:42,470 --> 00:16:44,660
