275
00:17:46,330 --> 00:17:49,840
"I have actually fallen for you
a long time ago."

276
00:17:53,700 --> 00:17:55,350
When reading the letter
from this listener,

277
00:17:55,430 --> 00:17:57,070
I can't help feeling a sense of

278
