304
00:20:17,990 --> 00:20:19,030
I just...

305
00:20:22,840 --> 00:20:25,390
Wu Yan. Do you still love him?

306
00:20:28,670 --> 00:20:29,510
I don't know.

307
00:20:29,590 --> 00:20:31,620
Why do you keep his card
