00:33:02,840 --> 00:33:03,960
She fell asleep.

494
00:33:06,230 --> 00:33:07,620
You take the team to the restaurant.

495
00:33:08,300 --> 00:33:09,670
Give me a call when everything is ready.

496
00:33:09,900 --> 00:33:10,700
Okay.

